(222, 1, '2019-03-20 03:27:33', '2019-03-20 03:27:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you have this issue while having OPENCART file on your local server. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Issue on chrome </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":219} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&amp; on Firefox</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":220} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/image-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-220\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><br><strong>SOLUTIONS</strong><br><br>Go to your Config.php root/admin<br>and add  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ini_set(\'error_reporting\', \'E_COMPILE_ERROR|E_RECOVERABLE_ERROR|E_ERROR|E_CORE_ERROR\'); <br><br>tada !!! now you can see your opencart website :) ENJOY</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'This site can’t be reached - CHROME', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '216-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-20 03:27:33', '2019-03-20 03:27:33', '', 216, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/216-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(236, 1, '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>प्रहरीले बताएको छ कि तीन श्रीलंका चर्च र तीन होटल एक साथ विस्फोटक को नजिकै नजिकै हिट भयो, कम से कम 138 मान्छे को मृत्यु हो।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'श्रीलंका ईस्टर बमोजिम: चर्च र होटल्स मा ठूलो हतियार', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e0%a4%b6%e0%a5%8d%e0%a4%b0%e0%a5%80%e0%a4%b2%e0%a4%82%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%be-%e0%a4%88%e0%a4%b8%e0%a5%8d%e0%a4%9f%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%ac%e0%a4%ae%e0%a5%8b%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%bf%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%9a%e0%a4%b0', '', '', '2023-05-04 05:15:43', '2023-05-04 05:15:43', '', 0, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/?p=236', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(242, 1, '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '', 'SEE result publishing soon...', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'see-result-publishing-soon', '', '', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '', 0, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/?p=242', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(622, 1, '2023-07-16 16:24:09', '2023-07-16 16:24:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you want to stop procrastinating, keep this area of your brain functioning at its best.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For many of us, procrastination is a major problem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we declare we\'ll work on our objectives, go to the gym, or pick up some new abilities, we usually end up watching Netflix. I have a history of procrastination as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Even though I had large plans and ambitions, not much was getting accomplished on a daily basis.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most individuals believe that procrastination results from indulging in bad habits, being lazy, or lacking motivation. However, it turns out that procrastination has neurological underpinnings. It is the end result of an ongoing conflict between the prefrontal cortex and limbic system in our brains.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The frontal lobe.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>The prefrontal cortex is the rational and analytical region of the brain in charge of decision-making, self-control, and planning for the future.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As noted by Dr. Joseph Ferrari, a renowned procrastination research specialist, in Still Procrastinating:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The prefrontal cortex, a region of the brain, controls our capacity to control behavior, including our ability to withstand the lure of instant gratification in favor of long-term advantages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In summary, the prefrontal cortex recognizes the value of postponing gratification in order to build a better future and assists in controlling our desires.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Maintaining this area of your brain in good shape is crucial if you want to avoid procrastinating (more on that later).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to Eliminate Procrastination? ( Neuroscience)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '618-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-07-16 16:24:09', '2023-07-16 16:24:09', '', 618, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?p=622', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(231, 1, '2019-04-11 12:14:00', '2019-04-11 12:14:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nepal Telecommunications Authority has ban banned public sports in Nepal. At the special request of the Central Research Bureau of Police, the Authority has directed all Internet service providers to close the public game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pubg Banned in Nepal. WHY?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pubg-banned-in-nepal-why', '', '', '2019-04-11 12:15:21', '2019-04-11 12:15:21', '', 0, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/?p=231', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(240, 1, '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>प्रहरीले बताएको छ कि तीन श्रीलंका चर्च र तीन होटल एक साथ विस्फोटक को नजिकै नजिकै हिट भयो, कम से कम 138 मान्छे को मृत्यु हो।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'श्रीलंका ईस्टर बमोजिम: चर्च र होटल्स मा ठूलो हतियार', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '236-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '2019-04-21 07:37:22', '', 236, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/236-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(279, 1, '2020-08-18 01:58:12', '2020-08-18 01:58:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For installing laravel passport make sure you add this line to <strong><em>config/app.php</em></strong> in the providers array (package service providers section):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Laravel\\Passport\\PassportServiceProvider::class,</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Then install the package and migrate the database</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>composer require laravel/passport<br>php artisan migrate<br>php artisan passport:install</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Clearing out the cache is generally helpful first step when commands are not working, especially when you update anything in the config folder on .env files.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>php artisan config:clear<br>php artisan config:cache</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Config clear removes the configuration cache file. Config cache creates a new configuration cache file with the current settings. Config cache enables faster load times for your apps!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'No Commands defined \"Passport\" Laravel 7', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'no-commands-defined-passport-laravel-7', '', '', '2020-08-18 01:58:25', '2020-08-18 01:58:25', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?p=279', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(245, 1, '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '', 'SEE result publishing soon...', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '242-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '2019-05-20 10:36:31', '', 242, 'http://ayushshrestha.com.np/blog/242-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2019-09-13 07:16:12', '2019-09-13 07:16:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Problem?</strong><br><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\n2</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I failed to run&nbsp;<code>node-sass</code>(node module), where I was able to setup path for input&nbsp;<code>extensions.scss</code>files and output files generated after compiling to&nbsp;<code>dist/</code>&nbsp;folder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now, I am using vscode extension&nbsp;<code>live sass compiler</code>,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>at bottom bar, when I clicked&nbsp;<code>Watched Sass</code>&nbsp;then it compiled automatically&nbsp;<code>scss</code>&nbsp;file to&nbsp;<code>css</code>&nbsp;but in same folder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><code>main.scss</code>&nbsp;is compiled to&nbsp;<code>main.css</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/w1A29.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/w1A29.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>problem is that I wanted to create that&nbsp;<code>compiled css</code>&nbsp;file in other folder .i.e. in output folder&nbsp;<code>./dist/</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have manually created&nbsp;<code>main.css</code>&nbsp;file in&nbsp;<code>./dist/folder</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How can I setup path to source and destination files in that extension?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Solutions</strong><br><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have had the same issue when I started implementing SMACSS methodology to my projects. This is the solution I have tried. hope it will help you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/yvHPe.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/yvHPe.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Go to VScode User Settings --&gt; Select \"Live Sass Compiler Config --&gt; add</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>\"liveSassCompile.settings.formats\": [{\n        \"format\": \"expanded\",\n        \"extensionName\": \".css\",\n        \"savePath\": \"./css\"\n    }]\n</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Gho7y.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Gho7y.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MORE DETAILS https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51696892/how-to-setup-output-path-to-compiled-css-files-using-vscode-live-sass-compiler<br><br>or on Visual Studio code<br><br>https://github.com/ritwickdey/vscode-live-sass-compiler/blob/master/docs/settings.md</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>https://github.com/ritwickdey/vscode-live-sass-compiler/blob/master/docs/settings.md</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CORRECTIONS</strong><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\n{    \"liveServer.settings.donotVerifyTags\": true,    \"workbench.editor.highlightModifiedTabs\": true,    \"editor.wordWrap\": \"on\",            \"liveSassCompile.settings.formats\": [{        \"format\": \"compressed\",        \"extensionName\": \".css\",        \"savePath\": \"./css\"    }],\"explorer.confirmDelete\": false<br>}\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to setup output path to compiled css files using `vscode live sass compiler extension` in windows10?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '172-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-09-13 07:16:12', '2019-09-13 07:16:12', '', 172, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/172-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(250, 1, '2019-09-13 08:16:33', '2019-09-13 08:16:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Problem?</strong><br><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\n2</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I failed to run&nbsp;<code>node-sass</code>(node module), where I was able to setup path for input&nbsp;<code>extensions.scss</code>files and output files generated after compiling to&nbsp;<code>dist/</code>&nbsp;folder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now, I am using vscode extension&nbsp;<code>live sass compiler</code>,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>at bottom bar, when I clicked&nbsp;<code>Watched Sass</code>&nbsp;then it compiled automatically&nbsp;<code>scss</code>&nbsp;file to&nbsp;<code>css</code>&nbsp;but in same folder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><code>main.scss</code>&nbsp;is compiled to&nbsp;<code>main.css</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/w1A29.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/w1A29.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>problem is that I wanted to create that&nbsp;<code>compiled css</code>&nbsp;file in other folder .i.e. in output folder&nbsp;<code>./dist/</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have manually created&nbsp;<code>main.css</code>&nbsp;file in&nbsp;<code>./dist/folder</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How can I setup path to source and destination files in that extension?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Solutions</strong><br><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have had the same issue when I started implementing SMACSS methodology to my projects. This is the solution I have tried. hope it will help you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/yvHPe.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/yvHPe.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Go to VScode User Settings --&gt; Select \"Live Sass Compiler Config --&gt; add</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>\"liveSassCompile.settings.formats\": [{\n        \"format\": \"expanded\",\n        \"extensionName\": \".css\",\n        \"savePath\": \"./css\"\n    }]\n</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Gho7y.png\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/Gho7y.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></a><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MORE DETAILS https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51696892/how-to-setup-output-path-to-compiled-css-files-using-vscode-live-sass-compiler<br><br>or on Visual Studio code<br><br>https://github.com/ritwickdey/vscode-live-sass-compiler/blob/master/docs/settings.md</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>https://github.com/ritwickdey/vscode-live-sass-compiler/blob/master/docs/settings.md</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CORRECTIONS</strong><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n{\n    \"liveServer.settings.donotVerifyTags\": true,\n    \"workbench.editor.highlightModifiedTabs\": true,\n    \"editor.wordWrap\": \"on\",\n    \n    \n    \"liveSassCompile.settings.formats\": [{\n        \"format\": \"compressed\",\n        \"extensionName\": \".css\",\n        \"savePath\": \"./css\"\n    }\n],\n\"explorer.confirmDelete\": false\n\n}\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'How to setup output path to compiled css files using `vscode live sass compiler extension` in windows10?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '172-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-09-13 08:16:33', '2019-09-13 08:16:33', '', 172, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/172-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(252, 1, '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>while you add chatbot message box in your website it it didnt work if you check console and it says that </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":253} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image-1024x85.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-253\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Refused to display \'https://www.facebook.com/v2.12/plugins/customerchat.php?app_id=&amp;attribution=setup_tool&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter.php%3Fversion%3D44%23cb%3Df13ed322c49f5e%26domain%3Dwww.floristnepal.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.floristnepal.com%252Ff173aec3cd4b68%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;page_id=398777027226348&amp;sdk=joey\' in a frame because an ancestor violates the following Content Security Policy directive: \"frame-ancestors https://www.facebook.com\".<br> about:blank:1 Refused to display \'https://www.facebook.com/v2.12/plugins/customerchat.php?app_id=&amp;attribution=setup_tool&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter.php%3Fversion%3D44%23cb%3Df13ed322c49f5e%26domain%3Dwww.floristnepal.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.floristnepal.com%252Ff173aec3cd4b68%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;page_id=398777027226348&amp;sdk=joey\' in a frame because an ancestor violates the following Content Security Policy directive: \"frame-ancestors https://www.facebook.com\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SOLUTION</strong> :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should whitelist your domain https://developers.facebook.com/docs/messenger-platform/messenger-profile/domain-whitelisting</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Click Settings at the top of your Page</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Click Messenger Platform on the left</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Edit whitelisted domains for your page in the Whitelisted Domains section</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Violates the following Content Security Policy - Messenger Chatbot in your website', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'violates-the-following-content-security-policy-messenger-chatbot-in-your-website', '', '', '2023-05-04 05:14:46', '2023-05-04 05:14:46', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?p=252', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(255, 1, '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>while you add chatbot message box in your website it it didnt work if you check console and it says that </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":253} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image-1024x85.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-253\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Refused to display \'https://www.facebook.com/v2.12/plugins/customerchat.php?app_id=&amp;attribution=setup_tool&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter.php%3Fversion%3D44%23cb%3Df13ed322c49f5e%26domain%3Dwww.floristnepal.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.floristnepal.com%252Ff173aec3cd4b68%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;page_id=398777027226348&amp;sdk=joey\' in a frame because an ancestor violates the following Content Security Policy directive: \"frame-ancestors https://www.facebook.com\".<br> about:blank:1 Refused to display \'https://www.facebook.com/v2.12/plugins/customerchat.php?app_id=&amp;attribution=setup_tool&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter.php%3Fversion%3D44%23cb%3Df13ed322c49f5e%26domain%3Dwww.floristnepal.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.floristnepal.com%252Ff173aec3cd4b68%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;page_id=398777027226348&amp;sdk=joey\' in a frame because an ancestor violates the following Content Security Policy directive: \"frame-ancestors https://www.facebook.com\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SOLUTION</strong> :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should whitelist your domain https://developers.facebook.com/docs/messenger-platform/messenger-profile/domain-whitelisting</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Click Settings at the top of your Page</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Click Messenger Platform on the left</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Edit whitelisted domains for your page in the Whitelisted Domains section</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Violates the following Content Security Policy - Messenger Chatbot in your website', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '2019-12-14 09:39:27', '', 252, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(257, 1, '2019-12-26 08:06:47', '2019-12-26 08:06:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Selection Sharer is a mobile-friendly social share plugin that shows a floating popover that allows highlighted/selected text to be shared on Facebook, LinkedIn or via email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On mobile devices, instead of better user experiences, the plugin will screen a social sharing popunder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It also has the ability, when a Facebook App ID is given, to display the Facebook sharing link inside the share popover.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Plugin has been used on Nepal Magazine, Medium, and The Kathmandu Post</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How to use ?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To use this plugin, you need to make sure \"selection-sharer.css\", \"jQuery\" &amp; \"selection-sharer.js\" files are included correctly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">&lt;script src=\"//code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"selection-sharer.css\"&gt;\n&lt;script src=\"selection-sharer.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 2. Specify the Facebook App ID in the meta tags (OPTIONAL). </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">&lt;meta property=\"fb:app_id\" content=\"CONTENT HERE\"&gt;\n&lt;meta property=\"fb:admins\" content=\"CONTENT HERE\"&gt;</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Then initialize the plugin on the target text content and done.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">$(\'p\').selectionSharer();</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.  Or ... </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">var sharer = new SelectionSharer(\'p\');</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Override the default CSS rules to create your own styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">#selectionSharerPopover:after {\n  content: \'\';\n  display: block;\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: -3px;\n  left: 50%;\n  margin-left: -4px;\n  width: 8px;\n  height: 8px;\n  -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg);\n  transform: rotate(45deg);\n  background: #262625;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 2px #262625;\n}\n\n#selectionSharerPopunder {\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 0px;\n  transition: height 0.5s ease-in-out;\n  background: #ccc;\n  border: none;\n  box-shadow: inset 0px 10px 5px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0px -10px 5px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n  border-radius: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jqueryscript.net/demo/Share-Selected-Text-On-Twitter-Email-jQuery-Selection-Sharer/\">DEMO</a>           <a href=\"https://www.jqueryscript.net/download/Share-Selected-Text-On-Twitter-Email-jQuery-Selection-Sharer.zip\">DOWNLOAD</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Selected TEXT share in Social ( Facebook, Twitter, Email)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'selected-text-share-in-social-facebook-twitter-email', '', '', '2023-05-04 05:13:42', '2023-05-04 05:13:42', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?p=257', 0, 'post', '', 0),
