 have happened.</li><li>Your database can be compromised if you install a poorly coded plugin.</li><li>A strong traffic spike may be encountered by your website, which is beyond the capability of your server.</li><li>Your WordPress web hosting may be at fault and because of some issue at its end, the database is not running.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I advise you to make a backup before any attempt to fix the error creating a database link in WordPress! To make a backup, you have the following choices:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to Repair a WordPress Database Connection?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '284-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-16 16:28:30', '2021-01-16 16:28:30', '', 284, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/284-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
