(383, 1, '2022-06-25 11:34:40', '2022-06-25 11:34:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Founded in January 2013, MyKronoz is a Swiss company headquartered in Geneva that designs and develops wearable devices to expand and facilitate the connected experience of the smart generation. MyKronoz offers a full range of affordable and stylish wearables, spanning across 4 product categories: activity trackers, smartwatches, hybrid smartwatches and true wireless earphones, all compatible with iOS and Android.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'MyKronoz', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mykronoz', '', '', '2023-07-18 05:34:57', '2023-07-18 05:34:57', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=383', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
