(407, 1, '2022-06-27 15:20:13', '2022-06-27 15:20:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nepal Magazine is Nepal\'s no 1 Weekly magazine and Nepal Magazine\'s official website. Nepal weekly is the country’s fastest growing socio-political news magazine, famous especially for acute political reporting and analysis. Nepal’s weekly circulation figures are at 37,000 copies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nepal Magazine', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nepal-magazine', '', '', '2023-07-18 05:34:43', '2023-07-18 05:34:43', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=407', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
